402
00:17:40,140 --> 00:17:41,800
She just didn't want to see me.

403
00:17:43,140 --> 00:17:44,140
Later,

404
00:17:45,020 --> 00:17:45,900
I thought

405
00:17:46,460 --> 00:17:48,140
even if she could forgive me,

406
00:17:48,260 --> 00:17:49,340
what's the use?

407
00:17:53,900 --> 00:17:56,630
I can't even give her the basic sense of security.

408
00:17:57,690 --> 00:17:58,660
So I thought

409
00:17:59,660 --> 00:18:00,700
maybe I should

410
00:18:01,580 --> 00:18:02,620
let her go.

411
00:18:03,820 --> 00:18:05,740
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

412
00:18:05,740 --> 00:18:07,770
I've been cursing you for her for over a year.

413
00:18:07,770 --> 00:18:10,770
That was basically the first thing I did when I woke up.

414
00:18:11,500 --> 00:18:12,380
It's fine.

415
00:18:13,140 --> 00:18:14,060
No matter what the reason is,

416
00:18:14,060 --> 00:18:15,500
