421
00:18:26,180 --> 00:18:27,910
She must be disappointed in me.

422
00:18:31,180 --> 00:18:32,020
Let me ask you.

423
00:18:32,060 --> 00:18:34,620
What's the biggest obstacle in a long-distance relationship?

424
00:18:34,620 --> 00:18:35,290
You.

425
00:18:35,290 --> 00:18:35,940
Answer me.

426
00:18:37,660 --> 00:18:39,060
The lack

427
00:18:39,620 --> 00:18:41,020
of the sense of security?

428
00:18:41,860 --> 00:18:42,500
You.

429
00:18:43,090 --> 00:18:44,090
How should I know?

430
00:18:44,180 --> 00:18:46,180
I've never been in a long-distance relationship.

431
00:18:46,180 --> 00:18:48,500
The sense of security doesn't matter.

432
00:18:48,500 --> 00:18:50,820
What you need is communication.

433
00:18:50,940 --> 00:18:51,980
Between you and Jiang Juanjuan,

434
00:18:51,980 --> 00:18:53,780
one was afraid that the other would be unhappy,

435
00:18:53,780 --> 00:18:55,780
and one was afraid that the other would be disappointed.

436
00:18:55,780 --> 00:18:58,010
Actually, you both got it wrong.

437
00:18:58,980 --> 00:19:01,660
I hope you have a new relationship soon.

438
00:19:02,060 --> 00:19:03,580
Never have a long-distance relationship again.

439
00:19:03,580 --> 00:19:04,900
So insecure.

440
00:19:07,780 --> 00:19:08,900
Actually, I think

441
00:19:09,180 --> 00:19:10,540
the lack of the sense of security,

442
00:19:10,540 --> 00:19:12,540
immaturity, and being unreasonable

443
00:19:12,540 --> 00:19:13,900
are nothing.

444
00:19:14,780 --> 00:19:15,660
In fact,

445
00:19:15,900 --> 00:19:17,540
the most serious thing is

446
00:19:18,180 --> 00:19:20,580
if I understand and care about him too much,

447
00:19:20,660 --> 00:19:22,460
I'll lose balance in mentality.

448
00:19:22,700 --> 00:19:25,300
I felt very uncomfortable,

449
00:19:25,660 --> 00:19:27,060
but I had to put up with it.

450
00:19:29,730 --> 00:19:33,660
And I would make a fuss about who cares more.

451
00:19:35,220 --> 00:19:36,690
Sometimes I was wondering

452
00:19:37,180 --> 00:19:40,180
if Jia Siwen took my understanding

453
00:19:40,180 --> 00:19:41,900
for granted.

454
00:19:43,940 --> 00:19:45,700
Then you should have told him.

455
00:19:46,700 --> 00:19:49,620
I was afraid that if I told him, he would think I'm immature

456
00:19:49,620 --> 00:19:50,660
and petty.

457
00:19:52,740 --> 00:19:54,780
Besides, this kind of thing can't simply be explained

458
00:19:54,780 --> 00:19:56,500
on the phone.

459
00:19:58,300 --> 00:19:59,810
What if we got impulsive

460
00:20:00,010 --> 00:20:01,780
