468
00:20:17,700 --> 00:20:21,060
And I would generously say it's okay.

469
00:20:23,260 --> 00:20:24,260
And then

470
00:20:24,260 --> 00:20:26,590
there would be more apologies between us.

471
00:20:29,650 --> 00:20:31,300
One day, I suddenly realized

472
00:20:31,420 --> 00:20:34,540
if I keep putting up with him,

473
00:20:34,700 --> 00:20:37,700
